description: Fantastic 2-bed condo on M Street is ideally located directly across from Medal of Honor Park in S. Boston's East Side! Inviting floor plan in sun splashed living/dining area overlooks the park through several front facing windows and comes complete with gas fireplace and speakers.  A tastefully appointed cook's kitchen features granite countertops, Jenn-Air stainless-steel appliances including six-burner range, and ample cabinetry throughout. Retreat to the bright and airy oversized primary bedroom with walk-in closet, en-suite bath w/ walk-in shower, and private deck. A generous 2nd bedroom, 2nd full bath, 1 direct access deeded parking spot, private storage, hardwood flooring throughout, in-unit laundry, & central a/c round out this special home!
